nz.ac.vuw.ecs.swen225.gp20.persistence

Class State

  • java.lang.Object
    • nz.ac.vuw.ecs.swen225.gp20.persistence.State

  • class State
extends java.lang.Object
    This class collects all the data required to save and load game states in a class to be easily serialised altogether using the GSON library.
